■書籍概要<br /><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/ASIN/4478022399/book2ch-22/\" target=\"_blank\">コンセプトのつくりかた </a><br /><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/ASIN/4478022399/book2ch-22/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51FKIE2%2BUNL._SL500_.jpg\" alt=\"4478022399\" border=\"0\" /></a><br />
