●一緒に読みたい本</p><p><br /><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/ASIN/4905042097/book2ch-22/\" target=\"_blank\">「週４時間」だけ働く。 </a><br /><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/ASIN/4905042097/book2ch-22/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://ec2.images-amazon.com/images/I/41Jf1s7EVAL._SL160_.jpg\" alt=\"4905042097\" border=\"0\" /></a><br />
